<div class="o2f-v2" id="o2fV2"><div class="o2f-bg" id="o2fBg"></div><nav class="dock"><a href="#hero" class="active">Home</a><a href="#coach">Coach</a><a href="#programs">Programs</a><a href="#results">Results</a><a href="#plans">Plans</a><a href="#contact">Start</a></nav><main class="o2f-main"><section class="section hero" id="hero"><div class="container"><span class="kicker">Coach Osama Omran — O2F Life</span><h1>Transform your body with a clear, guided system.</h1><p class="lead">Personalized coaching that combines training, nutrition, wellness direction, and real follow-up — built around your body, lifestyle, and goals.</p><div class="btns"><a class="btn primary" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Start your transformation</a><a class="btn" href="#programs">Explore programs</a></div><div class="journey"><article class="glass journey-card"><span class="num">1</span><b>Choose your goal</b><p>Training transformation, anti-aging guidance, or Methylene Blue education.</p></article><article class="glass journey-card"><span class="num">2</span><b>Get a clear plan</b><p>Training, nutrition, lifestyle, and follow-up are connected in one route.</p></article><article class="glass journey-card"><span class="num">3</span><b>Start with support</b><p>Clear next steps, direct guidance, and a practical system to follow.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section" id="coach"><div class="grid2 container"><div class="coach-photo glass"><img src="/assets/images/hero.jpeg" alt="Coach Osama Omran"><div class="stats"><span>20+<br><small>Years</small></span><span>1000+<br><small>Clients</small></span><span>100%<br><small>Custom</small></span><span>24/7<br><small>Support</small></span></div></div><article class="panel glass"><span class="kicker">Who is Osama Omran?</span><h2>The coach behind the O2F system.</h2><p>Osama Omran focuses on body transformation through a connected system that combines training, nutrition guidance, wellness direction, and practical follow-up. His approach is built around clarity, sustainability, and real progress — not random advice or short-term motivation.</p><div class="chips"><span class="chip">Personalized plans</span><span class="chip">Training + Nutrition</span><span class="chip">Follow-up</span><span class="chip">Sustainable habits</span></div><a class="btn primary" href="#how">See how it works</a></article></div></section><section class="section" id="programs"><div class="container"><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">Choose your path</span><h2>Three clear routes inside one transformation system.</h2><p>Each program explains who it is for, what it includes, and what the visitor should expect.</p></div><div class="tabs-shell glass"><div class="tabs-nav"><button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="anti" type="button">Anti-Aging</button><button class="tab-btn" data-tab="blue" type="button">Methylene Blue</button><button class="tab-btn" data-tab="training" type="button">Training Transformation</button></div><article class="tab-panel active" id="tab-anti"><div class="tab-copy glass"><span class="kicker">Long-term vitality</span><h3>Anti-Aging & Long-Term Vitality</h3><p>A guided route focused on recovery, vitality, sustainable habits, and better daily performance.</p><div class="cards3"><div class="mini"><b>For whom?</b><span>People who want more energy, better recovery, and a healthier routine.</span></div><div class="mini"><b>Includes</b><span>Lifestyle assessment, recovery direction, nutrition support, and follow-up.</span></div><div class="mini"><b>Expected result</b><span>A clearer routine that supports vitality and consistency.</span></div></div></div><div class="visual glass"><div class="symbol infinity">∞</div><div class="visual-caption"><b>Continuity and vitality</b><p>A visual language built around long-term balance.</p></div></div></article><article class="tab-panel" id="tab-blue"><div class="tab-copy glass"><span class="kicker">Education first</span><h3>Methylene Blue Education & Guidance</h3><p>A simple educational route that explains the idea clearly and guides the visitor toward the right next step.</p><div class="cards3"><div class="mini"><b>For whom?</b><span>People interested in focus, energy, and cellular-performance concepts.</span></div><div class="mini"><b>Includes</b><span>Simple explanation, guided understanding, and consultation-first direction.</span></div><div class="mini"><b>Safe next step</b><span>Ask, explore, and move forward with guidance instead of guessing.</span></div></div></div><div class="visual glass"><div class="molecule"></div><div class="visual-caption"><b>Scientific but simple</b><p>Molecule-inspired motion without confusing medical-heavy visuals.</p></div></div></article><article class="tab-panel" id="tab-training"><div class="tab-copy glass"><span class="kicker">Visible transformation</span><h3>Training Transformation</h3><p>A structured route that combines training, nutrition, and follow-up to drive visible physical transformation.</p><div class="cards3"><div class="mini"><b>For whom?</b><span>Beginners, returning trainees, and people who need clear structure.</span></div><div class="mini"><b>Includes</b><span>Training plan, nutrition direction, weekly tracking, and adjustments.</span></div><div class="mini"><b>Goal examples</b><span>Fat loss, muscle gain, recomposition, strength, and discipline.</span></div></div></div><div class="visual glass"><div class="motion-lines"></div><div class="visual-caption"><b>Movement and discipline</b><p>A clearer visual for training, progress, and action.</p></div></div></article></div></div></section><section class="section" id="how"><div class="container"><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">How it works</span><h2>Simple process, clear next steps.</h2></div><div class="steps"><article class="glass"><span class="num">1</span><h3>Assessment</h3><p>Your goal, body, lifestyle, and current level are reviewed first.</p></article><article class="glass"><span class="num">2</span><h3>Personalized plan</h3><p>You receive a route built around training, nutrition, and the support you need.</p></article><article class="glass"><span class="num">3</span><h3>Follow-up</h3><p>The plan evolves with your progress so the transformation stays realistic.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section" id="results"><div class="container before-wrap"><div class="ba glass"><div class="ba-card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517838277536-f5f99be501cd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=85" alt="Before"><span class="label">Before / Week 1</span></div><div class="ba-card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605296867304-46d5465a13f1?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=85" alt="After"><span class="label">After / Week 12</span></div></div><div><span class="kicker">Before & After</span><h2>Visible progress with a structured system.</h2><p>Results come from clear planning, consistent follow-up, and practical adjustments over time.</p><div class="result-list"><article class="glass result-card"><strong>1</strong><p>Clear tracking from the beginning.</p></article><article class="glass result-card"><strong>2</strong><p>Weekly follow-up and plan adjustments.</p></article><article class="glass result-card"><strong>3</strong><p>Training and nutrition aligned together.</p></article></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="plans"><div class="container"><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">Plans</span><h2>Choose the level that matches your goal.</h2><p>Every card explains who it is for, what it includes, and how to subscribe.</p></div><div class="plans"><article class="glass plan"><span class="kicker">Starter</span><h3>Basic Plan</h3><p>For people who need a clean first step with training and nutrition direction.</p><ul class="features"><li>Training direction</li><li>Nutrition guidance</li><li>Progress checkpoints</li><li>Simple weekly structure</li></ul><a class="btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Subscribe now</a></article><article class="glass plan highlight"><span class="kicker">Most popular</span><h3>Standard Plan</h3><p>The balanced option for stronger follow-up and a more complete route.</p><ul class="features"><li>Training plan</li><li>Nutrition direction</li><li>Weekly adjustments</li><li>Progress tracking</li><li>Clear action steps</li></ul><a class="btn primary" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Subscribe now</a></article><article class="glass plan"><span class="kicker">Advanced</span><h3>Premium Plan</h3><p>For deeper follow-up, premium guidance, and stronger accountability.</p><ul class="features"><li>Full transformation plan</li><li>Detailed monitoring</li><li>Lifestyle optimization</li><li>Advanced support</li><li>Higher accountability</li></ul><a class="btn" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Subscribe now</a></article></div></div></section><section class="section" id="stories"><div class="container"><div class="section-head"><span class="kicker">What clients say</span><h2>Real feedback that builds trust.</h2></div><div class="comments"><article class="glass"><div class="quote">“</div><h3>Clear and easy</h3><p>The plan felt organized and realistic. I knew exactly what to do every week.</p><span class="avatar">A</span></article><article class="glass"><div class="quote">“</div><h3>Visible progress</h3><p>The follow-up made the difference. The plan changed when my body changed.</p><span class="avatar">M</span></article><article class="glass"><div class="quote">“</div><h3>Premium guidance</h3><p>Training, nutrition, and support were connected in one simple system.</p><span class="avatar">S</span></article></div></div></section><section class="section final" id="contact"><div class="container grid2"><article class="glass panel"><span class="kicker">Start now</span><h2>Ready to start your transformation?</h2><p>Choose the path that fits your goal, and start with a system built around clarity, support, and real follow-up.</p><div class="btns"><a class="btn primary" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfafiMRn5PggOY8Ks4TcE70pji2zJx78yPpIVp5I9RQc6sIIQ/viewform?usp=header">Contact and subscribe</a><a class="btn" href="#plans">View plans</a></div></article><div class="faq"><article class="glass"><h3>Is this only training?</h3><p>No. It connects training, nutrition, wellness direction, and follow-up.</p></article><article class="glass"><h3>Not sure where to start?</h3><p>Send your goal and current level, and the suitable route can be selected.</p></article></div></div></section></main></div><script>(function(){var root=document.getElementById('o2fV2');var bg=document.getElementById('o2fBg');var tabs=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn'));var panels=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.tab-panel'));var dock=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.dock a'));var sections=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('.section[id]'));function fx(){var max=root.offsetHeight-window.innerHeight||1;var p=Math.max(0,Math.min(1,scrollY/max));bg.style.setProperty('--bg-y',(-p*240)+'px');bg.style.setProperty('--bg-s',(1.14+p*.06).toFixed(3));var cur=sections[0];sections.forEach(function(s){var r=s.getBoundingClientRect();if(r.top<innerHeight*.45&&r.bottom>innerHeight*.2)cur=s});dock.forEach(function(a){a.classList.toggle('active',a.getAttribute('href')==='#'+cur.id)})}tabs.forEach(function(b){b.onclick=function(){var id='tab-'+b.dataset.tab;tabs.forEach(function(x){x.classList.toggle('active',x===b)});panels.forEach(function(p){p.classList.toggle('active',p.id===id)})}});dock.forEach(function(a){a.onclick=function(e){var el=document.querySelector(a.getAttribute('href'));if(el){e.preventDefault();el.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})}}});addEventListener('scroll',fx,{passive:true});addEventListener('resize',fx);fx()})();</script>
